Smart Sizes Shape to Fit You.,A WIRELESS WONDER - Seamless design with knit-in zones provide targeted support exactly where you need it, including a stay-in-place ribbed underband.,NO-SLIP STRAPS - Wider straps with our no-slip Comfort-U design for stay-in-place straps.,COOL COMFORT - Cool Comfort fabric helps wick moisture and keep you cool and comfortable.,DESIGN DETAILS - 2-ply, non-foam cups flex to adapt to your shape, while a V front and deep U back enhances your figure.,THE CLOSURE - Cushioned hook-and-eye spa close in back has an innovative gel designed to reduce irritation and three fit adjustments - so everything feels just right.
longdescription: Customers tell us this BaliÂ® ComfortFlex FitÂ® wireless bra is one of the most comfortable bras they've ever owned. It starts with smart sizing, which means that the super stretchy non-foam 2-ply cups flex to adapt to your shape, not vice versa. Knit-in zones provide targeted support exactly where you need it, including a ribbed underband. It offers a flattering V neckline and deep U back, with wider no-slip straps. A hook and eye spa closure with gel is designed to reduce irritation. And you'll love how this sleek, seamless wireless bra disappears under tees and other clingy clothes. If it's possible to fall in love with a bra, this might be the one.

longdescription: ZIPPED UP STYLE. This Wirefree Motion Control Bra with trendy front zipper offers maximum support and all-around comfort for all your high-intensity workouts.
